com.jfoenix.controls

Class JFXSnackbar

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.Node
      • javafx.scene.Parent
        • javafx.scene.Group
          • com.jfoenix.controls.JFXSnackbar
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget

    public class JFXSnackbar
extends javafx.scene.Group
    See Also:
    Snackbars & toasts

    The use of a javafx Popup or PopupContainer for notifications would seem intuitive but Popups are displayed in their own dedicated windows and alligning the popup window and handling window on top layering is more trouble then it is worth.
